txt.en: Although your victory came at great cost, you have triumphed over Shelob the Great, last child of Ungoliant. Although Ungwetári lives still, maimed and blinded in the depths of the Remmorchant, it is hoped she will never again trouble the peoples of Middle-earth.

Within the deepest darkness of the Remmorchant lies Shelob the Great, the last child of Ungoliant. Known to Lord Celeborn and learned Elves as Ungwetári, it is believed naught but her final defeat can ensure the safety of the peoples of Middle-earth.
